{
  "video_id": "O0ihGlsLL1Y",
  "title": "Why Pearls Are So Expensive | So Expensive",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 400.0,
      "end_time": 3130.0,
      "text": "Pearls have been a symbol of elegance"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3130.0,
      "end_time": 5490.0,
      "text": "and class for centuries."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 5490.0,
      "end_time": 8360.0,
      "text": "The Maharajas of India and European queens"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 8360.0,
      "end_time": 12370.0,
      "text": "adorned themselves with pearls, a symbol of their prestige."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 12370.0,
      "end_time": 16590.0,
      "text": "At 2018&#39;s Catholic Church-inspired Met Gala,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 16590.0,
      "end_time": 18119.0,
      "text": "celebrities walked the red carpet"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 18120.0,
      "end_time": 19530.0,
      "text": "dripping in pearls."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 19530.0,
      "end_time": 23910.0,
      "text": "Uma Thurman&#39;s dress had over 3,000 white pearls sewn to it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 23910.0,
      "end_time": 26150.0,
      "text": "while Rihanna&#39;s pope-inspired outfit"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 26150.0,
      "end_time": 28330.0,
      "text": "was encrusted in pearls."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 28330.0,
      "end_time": 31110.0,
      "text": "At the 2019 Grammys, Cardi B"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 31110.0,
      "end_time": 34890.0,
      "text": "was basically dressed like an oyster."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 34900.0,
      "end_time": 36240.0,
      "text": "The most expensive pearl ever sold"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 36240.0,
      "end_time": 38600.0,
      "text": "was Marie Antoinette&#39;s pendant."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 38600.0,
      "end_time": 43340.0,
      "text": "It sold for $32 million in a 2018 auction."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 43340.0,
      "end_time": 46483.0,
      "text": "But what is it that makes pearls so expensive?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53760.0,
      "end_time": 55610.0,
      "text": "Marie Antoinette&#39;s pearl was part"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55610.0,
      "end_time": 57577.0,
      "text": "of a diamond-studded pendant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57577.0,
      "end_time": 60580.0,
      "text": "and it has important historical significance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 60580.0,
      "end_time": 62960.0,
      "text": "which increased its value."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62960.0,
      "end_time": 64660.0,
      "text": "But there are several other factors"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 64660.0,
      "end_time": 66759.0,
      "text": "that determine the value of a pearl."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66760.0,
      "end_time": 68120.0,
      "text": "Tom Moses: Assessing the value of a pearl"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68120.0,
      "end_time": 71500.0,
      "text": "is probably the most complex gem to assess."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 71500.0,
      "end_time": 73110.0,
      "text": "Narrator: That&#39;s Tom Moses."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 73110.0,
      "end_time": 76740.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s a gemologist at the Gemological Institute of America"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76740.0,
      "end_time": 78800.0,
      "text": "where he oversees diamond grading,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 78800.0,
      "end_time": 82259.0,
      "text": "colored stone identification, and pearl identification."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 84300.0,
      "text": "He says that part of the reason"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 84300.0,
      "end_time": 86670.0,
      "text": "the Marie Antoinette pearl is worth so much"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 86670.0,
      "end_time": 89340.0,
      "text": "is because it&#39;s a natural pearl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 89340.0,
      "end_time": 91230.0,
      "text": "which brings us to one quality"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 91230.0,
      "end_time": 93450.0,
      "text": "that determines a pearl&#39;s value."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 93450.0,
      "end_time": 96340.0,
      "text": "Natural versus cultured."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 97940.0,
      "end_time": 100330.0,
      "text": "Natural pearls are hard to find."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 100330.0,
      "end_time": 103800.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re rare, and this makes them worth more money."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 103800.0,
      "end_time": 105780.0,
      "text": "But let&#39;s rewind for a second."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 105780.0,
      "end_time": 107800.0,
      "text": "What is a natural pearl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 107800.0,
      "end_time": 109830.0,
      "text": "and how are they formed?"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 109830.0,
      "end_time": 112600.0,
      "text": "Natural pearls form when some kind of irritant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 112600.0,
      "end_time": 114520.0,
      "text": "usually a small organism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 114520.0,
      "end_time": 117330.0,
      "text": "makes its way into the shell of a mollusk"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 117330.0,
      "end_time": 119450.0,
      "text": "like an oyster or a mussel."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 119450.0,
      "end_time": 121420.0,
      "text": "To protect itself from the invader,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 121420.0,
      "end_time": 124940.0,
      "text": "the mollusk starts to coat the debris with nacre,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 124940.0,
      "end_time": 127670.0,
      "text": "or mother-of-pearl, the same material"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 127670.0,
      "end_time": 130530.0,
      "text": "that lines the inner layer of its shell."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 130530.0,
      "end_time": 131810.0,
      "text": "It continues doing this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 131810.0,
      "end_time": 135430.0,
      "text": "and the irritant grows into a shiny pearl."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 135430.0,
      "end_time": 138640.0,
      "text": "Cultured pearls are formed by the same process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 138640.0,
      "end_time": 142589.0,
      "text": "but instead of the irritant entering the shell accidentally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 142590.0,
      "end_time": 145433.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s put there intentionally by a human."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 147000.0,
      "end_time": 150380.0,
      "text": "Pearl farmers insert a piece of mollusk tissue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 150380.0,
      "end_time": 151940.0,
      "text": "which is called donor tissue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 151940.0,
      "end_time": 153829.0,
      "text": "into the shell of the oyster"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 153830.0,
      "end_time": 155860.0,
      "text": "where they want the pearl to grow."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 155860.0,
      "end_time": 158340.0,
      "text": "This triggers the oyster&#39;s defense response,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 158340.0,
      "end_time": 161463.0,
      "text": "and it starts coating that piece of tissue with nacre."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 162440.0,
      "end_time": 164460.0,
      "text": "The vast majority of pearls on the market"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 164460.0,
      "end_time": 165933.0,
      "text": "are cultured pearls."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 166800.0,
      "end_time": 168550.0,
      "text": "The Gemological Institute of America"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 168550.0,
      "end_time": 173100.0,
      "text": "uses X-rays to tell if a pearl is natural or cultured."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 173100.0,
      "end_time": 175320.0,
      "text": "If you look closely at these two images,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 175320.0,
      "end_time": 176870.0,
      "text": "you can see the difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 176870.0,
      "end_time": 178890.0,
      "text": "Moses: Think about the layers of an onion."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 178890.0,
      "end_time": 180619.0,
      "text": "So a natural pearl would have all of those"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 180620.0,
      "end_time": 185610.0,
      "text": "concentric layers of growth from the very inside out."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 185610.0,
      "end_time": 187160.0,
      "text": "Narrator: A cultured pearl, on the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 187160.0,
      "end_time": 190500.0,
      "text": "is like an orange, with a large center"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 190500.0,
      "end_time": 193780.0,
      "text": "and a thinner layer of pearl growth around that."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 193780.0,
      "end_time": 196240.0,
      "text": "The large center is the manmade irritant"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 196240.0,
      "end_time": 199173.0,
      "text": "placed in the shell to encourage nacre formation."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 200400.0,
      "end_time": 203260.0,
      "text": "Cultured pearls date all the way back to around 500 AD"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 206795.0,
      "text": "in China. However, in 1893, the Japanese-born"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 206803.0,
      "end_time": 209550.0,
      "text": "K≈çkichi Mikimoto streamlined the process"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 209550.0,
      "end_time": 212930.0,
      "text": "and eventually created perfectly round pearls."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 212930.0,
      "end_time": 215130.0,
      "text": "Today, Mikimoto is widely considered"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 215130.0,
      "end_time": 217620.0,
      "text": "the grandfather of cultured pearls."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 217620.0,
      "end_time": 220470.0,
      "text": "He used Akoya pearls, which are the traditional"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 220470.0,
      "end_time": 223109.0,
      "text": "white round pearls you&#39;re probably familiar with."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 223110.0,
      "end_time": 225570.0,
      "text": "By the 1920s, cultured pearls became"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 225570.0,
      "end_time": 228380.0,
      "text": "more commercially available, which made them more affordable"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 228380.0,
      "end_time": 231300.0,
      "text": "and accessible to people who weren&#39;t royalty."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 231300.0,
      "end_time": 233370.0,
      "text": "But just because you can grow a cultured pearl"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 233370.0,
      "end_time": 236200.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t mean it&#39;s an easy process."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 236200.0,
      "end_time": 238580.0,
      "text": "Pearl farmers pry open the mollusk shell"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 238580.0,
      "end_time": 241270.0,
      "text": "just enough to implant the piece of foreign tissue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 241270.0,
      "end_time": 243700.0,
      "text": "then they put the oysters back in the water"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 243700.0,
      "end_time": 246619.0,
      "text": "and wait anywhere from six months to two years"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 246620.0,
      "end_time": 247930.0,
      "text": "for pearls to form,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 247930.0,
      "end_time": 250830.0,
      "text": "and not every pearl comes out the same,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 250830.0,
      "end_time": 252470.0,
      "text": "which brings us to another quality"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 252470.0,
      "end_time": 255350.0,
      "text": "that can make one pearl worth more than another."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 255350.0,
      "end_time": 256370.0,
      "text": "Size."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 256370.0,
      "end_time": 258310.0,
      "text": "The larger the pearl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 258310.0,
      "end_time": 260769.0,
      "text": "the more valuable, just like any other gem."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 260769.0,
      "end_time": 262729.0,
      "text": "Narrator: The size of the pearl largely depends"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 262730.0,
      "end_time": 264520.0,
      "text": "on the size of the mollusk."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 264520.0,
      "end_time": 266930.0,
      "text": "Certain oysters grow bigger than others"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 266930.0,
      "end_time": 269520.0,
      "text": "and can, therefore, make bigger pearls."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 269520.0,
      "end_time": 271700.0,
      "text": "For example, Akoya pearls can only grow"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 271700.0,
      "end_time": 274599.0,
      "text": "to about 9 or 10 millimeters in diameter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 274600.0,
      "end_time": 277380.0,
      "text": "but South Sea pearls and black Tahitian pearls"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 277380.0,
      "end_time": 281390.0,
      "text": "can reach a diameter of around 15 or 16 millimeters."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 281390.0,
      "end_time": 283630.0,
      "text": "The larger size makes South Sea pearls"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 283630.0,
      "end_time": 287240.0,
      "text": "and black pearls the most valuable type of pearl."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 287240.0,
      "end_time": 288790.0,
      "text": "On Mikimoto&#39;s website,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 288790.0,
      "end_time": 291630.0,
      "text": "this strand of South Sea cultured pearls"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 291630.0,
      "end_time": 295340.0,
      "text": "is selling for $32,000."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 295340.0,
      "end_time": 297659.0,
      "text": "The other notable difference between pearl types"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 297660.0,
      "end_time": 299430.0,
      "text": "is the color."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 299430.0,
      "end_time": 301680.0,
      "text": "Sometimes this goes hand in hand with size"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 301680.0,
      "end_time": 303930.0,
      "text": "because the pearl&#39;s color is determined"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 303930.0,
      "end_time": 306290.0,
      "text": "mostly by the mollusk it comes from."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 306290.0,
      "end_time": 309630.0,
      "text": "Tahitian black pearls are black because the inside"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 309630.0,
      "end_time": 313100.0,
      "text": "of the Pinctada margaritifera oyster is black,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 313100.0,
      "end_time": 314710.0,
      "text": "but colors can vary slightly"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 314710.0,
      "end_time": 317180.0,
      "text": "based on the culturing process as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 317180.0,
      "end_time": 319370.0,
      "text": "The main reason for the color difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 319370.0,
      "end_time": 322220.0,
      "text": "is the species of the mollusk."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 322220.0,
      "end_time": 324380.0,
      "text": "Another very interesting influence"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 324380.0,
      "end_time": 328110.0,
      "text": "is when a pearl is cultured,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 328110.0,
      "end_time": 331970.0,
      "text": "there is a donor tissue used from another living mollusk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 331970.0,
      "end_time": 335410.0,
      "text": "and depending on the color of that tissue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 335410.0,
      "end_time": 340220.0,
      "text": "it will influence the color of the final cultured pearl."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 340220.0,
      "end_time": 342830.0,
      "text": "Narrator: Take for example Akoya pearls."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 342830.0,
      "end_time": 344120.0,
      "text": "These are all white pearls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 344120.0,
      "end_time": 346950.0,
      "text": "but the shade of white can still vary."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 346950.0,
      "end_time": 349170.0,
      "text": "Some strands might be slightly more pink,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 349170.0,
      "end_time": 351763.0,
      "text": "while others have more of a greenish tint."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 352600.0,
      "end_time": 355340.0,
      "text": "Tom says that pinker pearls are typically preferred"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 355340.0,
      "end_time": 357330.0,
      "text": "over green hues."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 357330.0,
      "end_time": 359950.0,
      "text": "Along with size and color, the shape and surface"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 359950.0,
      "end_time": 362960.0,
      "text": "of a pearl can have an impact on its value."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 362960.0,
      "end_time": 365733.0,
      "text": "Typically the rounder and smoother, the better."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 366860.0,
      "end_time": 369410.0,
      "text": "And finally, perhaps the hardest variable"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 369410.0,
      "end_time": 372200.0,
      "text": "to measure: luster."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 372200.0,
      "end_time": 375550.0,
      "text": "Luster is essentially the way a pearl reflects light."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 375550.0,
      "end_time": 378200.0,
      "text": "The shinier the pearl, the better."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 378200.0,
      "end_time": 380719.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s hard to tell how shiny a pearl is"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 380720.0,
      "end_time": 383730.0,
      "text": "unless you have other pearls to compare it to."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 383730.0,
      "end_time": 386650.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why Tom and the rest of the Gemological Institute"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 386650.0,
      "end_time": 390310.0,
      "text": "have a collection of sample strands for comparison."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 390310.0,
      "end_time": 393700.0,
      "text": "That way they can look at how one strand of pearls"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 393700.0,
      "end_time": 395560.0,
      "text": "compares to another and see where it falls"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 395560.0,
      "end_time": 396613.0,
      "text": "on the luster scale."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 397660.0,
      "end_time": 399320.0,
      "text": "The quality of a pearl&#39;s luster"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 399320.0,
      "end_time": 403290.0,
      "text": "is influenced by the layers of nacre that coat the center."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 403290.0,
      "end_time": 404290.0,
      "text": "One way to think of it"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 404290.0,
      "end_time": 406230.0,
      "text": "is like the tiles of a roof."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 406870.0,
      "end_time": 409970.0,
      "text": "Picture a roof with all the tiles lined"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 409970.0,
      "end_time": 411989.0,
      "text": "up so that everything fits together well."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 411990.0,
      "end_time": 414100.0,
      "text": "If you translate that to a pearl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 414100.0,
      "end_time": 417160.0,
      "text": "it would result in a nice, high-luster pearl."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 417160.0,
      "end_time": 420500.0,
      "text": "A dull, low-luster pearl would be more like a roof"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 420500.0,
      "end_time": 423883.0,
      "text": "with broken and fragmented tiles that don&#39;t line up."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 425000.0,
      "end_time": 426340.0,
      "text": "When you take into consideration"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 426340.0,
      "end_time": 429280.0,
      "text": "all of these factors, finding or creating"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 429280.0,
      "end_time": 432000.0,
      "text": "the perfect pearl is an art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 432000.0,
      "end_time": 435500.0,
      "text": "and the fact remains they&#39;re grown inside an animal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 435500.0,
      "end_time": 437640.0,
      "text": "so it&#39;s impossible to have complete control"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 437640.0,
      "end_time": 440000.0,
      "text": "over how and when they form,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 440000.0,
      "end_time": 441450.0,
      "text": "especially in the wild."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 441450.0,
      "end_time": 443370.0,
      "text": "So if you ever bite down on something hard"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 443370.0,
      "end_time": 445350.0,
      "text": "while you&#39;re eating an oyster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 445350.0,
      "end_time": 447730.0,
      "text": "take a look at it before you chuck it."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 447730.0,
      "end_time": 450700.0,
      "text": "It might be more than a piece of sand."
    }
  ]
}